Interface GAIGSdatastr

All Known Implementing Classes:
GAIGSarray, GAIGSbase, GAIGSgraph, GAIGShashStruct, GAIGSlabel, GAIGSlegend, GAIGSlist, GAIGSMemoryManager, GAIGSNameValueIndex, GAIGSnewArray, GAIGSnewQueue, GAIGSnewStack, GAIGSphylogenetic_forest, GAIGSphylogenetic_tree, GAIGSprimitiveCollection, GAIGSqueue, GAIGSRefStruct, GAIGSstack, GAIGStext, GAIGStree
public interface GAIGSdatastr

The GAIGSdatastr interface provides constants used as default values for the name, color, position and font size of GAIGS structures. It requires methods for getting and setting the name of the structure, and a toXML method, which is used to generate the XML script for a structure.

Version:
6/20/06
Author:
Myles McNally
